<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《高昌》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汉风悲壮如歌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已西吹千年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火烧红的热土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落地生根</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人匆匆走远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过她生机依然</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>桑树园、桃儿沟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>瓜果香甜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吐鲁番的葡萄熟了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>来喝一口坎尔井的甘泉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有《西游记》的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎并不遥远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赏一曲维族舞吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里有幸福的生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甜蜜的事业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200813/97067f67e23f49d59e207cb485f39559.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
